Consign, at once and for keeps, Mrs. Sawyer1 to a mental asylum (this will give everybody more elbow room).

Cut out the pop art (Chag et a!) and replace it by a Book Review page once a week.





Faithfully yours,

Old Reader

Vladimir Nabokov





